structured.sql:
WITH __aicom_product AS (
  SELECT
    brand,
    category,
    channel,
    chnl_product_id,
    color,
    fit,
    gender,
    image_url,
    material,
    price,
    product_name,
    season,
    size,
    style_code,
    style_tags,
    subcategory,
    url
  FROM noa.agent_bigdata.aicom_product
)
SELECT
  brand,
  category,
  channel,
  chnl_product_id,
  color,
  fit,
  gender,
  image_url,
  material,
  price,
  product_name,
  season,
  size,
  style_code,
  style_tags,
  subcategory,
  url
FROM __aicom_product
WHERE
  brand = '로엠'
  AND (
    LOWER(product_name) LIKE '%기모%'
    OR LOWER(style_tags) LIKE '%기모%'
    OR LOWER(material) LIKE '%기모%'
  )
  AND (
    LOWER(product_name) LIKE '%긴팔%' OR LOWER(style_tags) LIKE '%긴팔%'
  )
LIMIT 50
 -- Generated by Cortex Analyst
;

    OR LOWER(style_tags) LIKE '%티셔츠%'
    OR LOWER(style_tags) LIKE '%t셔츠%'
  )

  AND price <= 39999
